content:
Build an Einstein Conversation Mining Report

Create Conversation Mining reports based on specific dates or fields on your channel record.

Einstein Conversation Mining is available in Lightning Experience with the Service Intelligence add-on.
Available in: Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To build and manage Einstein Conversation Mining reports:
	* Customize Application
	* Modify Metadata
	* Manage Bots

Einstein Conversation Mining requires at least 2,500 records with an identifiable contact reason after filters are applied to create a report.

To build a new Einstein Conversation Mining Report:
1. Click New Report.
2. Select a channel and give the report a name.
3. Define a date range for the report.
4. Choose Include All Conversations or Segment Conversations.
5. Filter out cases used for reasons other than customer support.
6. Click Build Report.

Your report builds in the background, ready when the status changes to completed. The report build time depends on dataset size, but most take around 24 hours.
title: Building Einstein Conversation Mining Reports in Service Cloud
